Comprehensive tests for WeSign Management API covering:
- Companies management (create, read, update, delete)
- Users management (login, list, reset password, update)
- Licenses management
- System configuration

Note: Management API uses separate authentication from User API.

- CompaniesController (7 endpoints)
- UsersController (6 endpoints)
- LicensesController
- ConfigurationController
- PaymentController
- ProgramsController
- ActiveDirectoryController
- OTPController
- ReportsController
- LogsController
